<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="164" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,1753,2030]" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1753,1778]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" reason="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Monotypic genus of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Topsent" authorityYear="1894" box="[525,643,1753,1778]" class="Demospongiae" family="Bubaridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Halichondrida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="family">Bubaridae</taxonomicName>
, characterized by stalked and flabellate body shape, possessing long hispidating styles and a plumoreticulate internal skeleton made of choanosomal rhabdostyles, oxeas, and strongyles, with smooth and spiny forms co-occurring. Microscleres are raphides in trichodragmata (genus diagnosis herein redefined after 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pulitzer-Finali" authorityYear="1983" box="[517,662,1861,1886]" class="Demospongiae" family="Bubaridae" genus="Rhabdobaris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Halichondrida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[517,662,1861,1886]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">Rhabdobaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
being restituted as a valid genus; not a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Topsent, 1898" authorityName="Topsent" authorityYear="1898" class="Demospongiae" family="Bubaridae" genus="Cerbaris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Halichondrida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1336,1436,1861,1886]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">Cerbaris</emphasis>
Topsent, 1898
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="164" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,1753,2030]" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1933,1958]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
See the &quot;Taxonomic remarks&quot; section of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pulitzer-Finali" authorityYear="1983" box="[779,1036,1933,1958]" class="Demospongiae" family="Bubaridae" genus="Rhabdobaris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Halichondrida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="implicata">
<emphasis box="[779,1036,1933,1958]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">Rhabdobaris implicata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for further discussion and concerns about the morphological affinity of the herein restituted genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pulitzer-Finali" authorityYear="1983" box="[936,1081,1969,1994]" class="Demospongiae" family="Bubaridae" genus="Rhabdobaris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Halichondrida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[936,1081,1969,1994]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="164">Rhabdobaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and members of the family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nardo" authorityYear="1833" box="[151,293,2005,2030]" class="Demospongiae" family="Raspailiidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poecilosclerida" pageId="23" pageNumber="164" phylum="Porifera" rank="family">Raspailiidae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
